Amish Girls Cc PST Those Amish Girls An Amish woman and her daughter were riding in an old buggy one cold blustery day The daughter said to her mother My hands are freezing cold The mother replied Put them between your legs Your body heat will warm them up So the daughter did and her hands warmed up The next day the daughter was riding with her boy friend and he said My hands are freezing cold The girl replied Put them between my legs The warmth of my body will warm them up So he did and warmed his hands The following day the boyfriend was again in the buggy with the daughter He said My nose is cold The girl replied Put it between my legs The warmth of my body will warm it up So he did and warmed his nose The next day the boyfriend was again driving with the daughter and he said My penis is frozen solid The following day the daughter was driving in the buggy with her mother and she says to her mother Have you ever heard of a penis Slightly concerned the mother said Why yes Why do you ask The daughter replies Well they make one hell of a mess when they defrost dont they
